==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: bounds
<hw>bounds</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the line or plane
indicating the limit or extent of something; <as>as, the football was
caught out of <ex>bounds</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> boundary, bound.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the greatest possible extent or degree of
something.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> limit, boundary.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bounteous</ent>⟦br⟧
